---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Visa Sponsored Tech Jobs in Spain | Software Engineering & More"
description: "Find visa-sponsored tech jobs in Spain with relocation assistance. Browse software engineering, data science, and product roles in Barcelona, Madrid and more."
permalink: /jobs-in-spain/
---

{% set country_name = "Spain" %}
{% set country_flag = "🇪🇸" %}
{% set grouped = jobs | groupByCountry %}
{% set countryJobs = grouped["Spain"] or [] %}

{% block structuredData %}
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
  "itemListElement": [
    { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "{{ site.url }}/" },
    { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Jobs by Country", "item": "{{ site.url }}/jobs-by-country/" },
    { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 3, "name": "Spain", "item": "{{ site.url }}/jobs-in-spain/" }
  ]
}
</script>
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "CollectionPage",
  "name": "Visa Sponsored Tech Jobs in Spain",
  "description": "Find {{ countryJobs | length }}+ visa-sponsored tech jobs in Spain with relocation assistance.",
  "url": "{{ site.url }}/jobs-in-spain/",
  "publisher": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "{{ site.name }}", "url": "{{ site.url }}" },
  "mainEntity": {
    "@type": "ItemList",
    "numberOfItems": {{ countryJobs | length }},
    "itemListElement": [
      {% for job in countryJobs | limit(10) %}
      {
        "@type": "ListItem",
        "position": {{ loop.index }},
        "item": {
          "@type": "JobPosting",
          "title": "{{ job.position }}",
          "datePosted": "{{ job.post_date }}",
          "description": "{{ job.position }} at {{ job.company }} in {{ job.location }}. Visa sponsorship and relocation assistance included.",
          "employmentType": "FULL_TIME",
          "hiringOrganization": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "{{ job.company }}",
            "logo": "{{ site.url }}{{ job.logo }}"
          },
          "jobLocation": {
            "@type": "Place",
            "address": { "@type": "PostalAddress", "addressCountry": "ES", "addressLocality": "{{ job.location }}" }
          },
          "url": "{{ job.description }}"
        }
      }{% if not loop.last %},{% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    ]
  }
}
</script>
{% endblock %}

{# Hero #}
<section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-brand-50 to-white dark:from-gray-900 dark:to-gray-950 py-12 md:py-16">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
    <nav class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-brand-600 dark:hover:text-brand-400 transition-colors">Home</a>
      <i data-lucide="chevron-right" class="w-3.5 h-3.5"></i>
      <a href="/jobs-by-country/" class="hover:text-brand-600 dark:hover:text-brand-400 transition-colors">Jobs by Country</a>
      <i data-lucide="chevron-right" class="w-3.5 h-3.5"></i>
      <span class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white font-medium">Spain</span>
    </nav>
    <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
      <span class="text-5xl">{{ country_flag }}</span>
      <div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 dark:text-white tracking-tight">
          Tech Jobs in Spain
        </h1>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-1">
          {{ countryJobs | length }} visa-sponsored positions with relocation assistance
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-6">
      <span class="badge badge-visa">Visa Sponsorship</span>
      <span class="badge badge-reloc">Relocation Assistance</span>
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
        <i data-lucide="map-pin" class="w-3.5 h-3.5"></i>
        Barcelona, Madrid & more
      </span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# Job Listings #}
<section class="py-12">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-6">
      <h2 class="section-heading">All Positions</h2>
      <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">{{ countryJobs | length }} jobs</span>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      {% for job in jobs %}
      {% if "Spain" in job.location %}
      <div class="job-card">
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-start gap-4">
          <img src="{{ job.logo }}" alt="{{ job.company }}" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg object-cover shrink-0" loading="lazy" onerror="this.src='/favicon/android-chrome-192x192.png'">
          <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-1">{{ job.position }}</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-2">{{ job.company }}</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-4 gap-y-1 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-3">
              <span class="flex items-center gap-1">
                <i data-lucide="map-pin" class="w-3.5 h-3.5"></i>
                {{ job.location }}
              </span>
              <span class="flex items-center gap-1">
                <i data-lucide="clock" class="w-3.5 h-3.5"></i>
                {{ job.post_date | timeAgo }}
              </span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              {% if job.reloc %}<span class="badge badge-reloc">{{ job.reloc }}</span>{% endif %}
              {% if job.visa %}<span class="badge badge-visa">{{ job.visa }}</span>{% endif %}
              <span class="badge badge-contract">{{ job.contract }}</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <a href="{{ job.description }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="job-card-apply">
            Apply <i data-lucide="external-link" class="w-3.5 h-3.5 ml-1.5"></i>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# SEO Content #}
<section class="py-12 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900/50">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
    <h2 class="section-heading">Working in Spain as a Tech Professional</h2>
    <p>
      Spain has emerged as one of Europe's most exciting tech destinations. Barcelona has grown into a major tech hub, hosting the annual Mobile World Congress and attracting companies from across the globe. Madrid is rapidly expanding its startup ecosystem, and cities like Valencia and Malaga are becoming popular for remote-friendly companies. Spain offers an unbeatable combination of lifestyle, climate, and growing career opportunities.
    </p>
    <p>
      For non-EU tech professionals, Spain offers several visa pathways including the <strong>Highly Qualified Professional visa</strong> and the newer <strong>Digital Nomad visa</strong> (introduced in 2023). Companies that sponsor visas typically handle the application process. Spain also participates in the EU Blue Card program. The cost of visa processing varies but is generally straightforward with employer sponsorship.
    </p>
    <p>
      While salaries in Spain are lower than in Northern Europe (typically €35,000–€65,000 for mid-to-senior engineers), the cost of living is significantly lower too, especially outside Barcelona and Madrid. Spain offers excellent healthcare, a Mediterranean lifestyle, and one of the best qualities of life in Europe. The growing number of international companies means English-only roles are increasingly common.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

